    <h1>UTM Parameters</h1>
    <p class="description">Tracking tags appended to URLs that tell Google Analytics exactly which campaign, channel, and creative sent each visitor. Without UTMs, <strong>most marketing traffic shows up as "direct" — invisible and unattributable</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
